Ramesses-of-the-First-Binding unified rival city-shrines under the Solar Court of the Undivided Disk.
He declared sunlight was law made visible: impartial, total, inescapable.
He conscripted the Keepers' road-taxation apparatus and scaled it into a theological instrument.
He commissioned the Great Pyramid as public machine of kingship, hidden soul-adjudication machine, and cosmic containment for the Black Sun Shard.
